These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, pear
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, trike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is not to the right of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | pomegranate   | pear   |
| Transport   | trike | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, 7up
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | 7up | water   |
| Sport      | baseball | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: mango, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, ambient
1. the person eating mango is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | strawberry | mango |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | ambient     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
